          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "From measured fission product activities ratios",
                "'R-values' calculated as",
                "R=a(99,235)*a(X,245)/(a(99,245)*a(X,235))",
                "  where 99,X,235 and 245 have the meaning explained",
                "  under method above.",
                "Yields for product X from fission of Cm-245 (=Y(X,245))",
                "are calculated as",
                "  Y(X,245)=R*Y(99,245)*Y(X,235)/Y(99,235), where",
                "Y(99,245) is an assumed value for the Cm-245 fission",
                "          yield of Mo-99",
                "Y(X,235) and Y(99,235) are the U-235 fission yields of",
                "         fission product X and Mo-99 respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
